description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

Kate and Leisha discuss clothes, reaching goals, living in a different country, writing their memoires, relaxing activities, and give advice on redoing floors and wedding guest lists.

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod
